snippet.title: talkRADIO
snippet.description:
Britain’s fastest growing radio station is now on your TV! Download the talkRADIO TV app and visit http://talkradio.tv/settings/how-to-watch for details how to watch.

Feedback: feedback@talkradio.co.uk
Footage requests: social.media@talkradio.co.uk

Ofcom regulates the editorial content of on-demand programme services. If you have complained
to us, and you are dissatisfied with our response, you can submit a complaint about our on-demand 
service to Ofcom using the online complaint form at:

http://stakeholders.ofcom.org.uk/broadcasting/on-demand/complain 

Advertising within our services is regulated by the Advertising Standards Authority. You can access
the ASA complaints procedures online at:

http://www.asa.org.uk/Complaints 

or by telephoning 020 7492 2222. 

Further information about Ofcom can be found at www.ofcom.org.uk, and about the ASA 
at www.asa.org.uk
